channel.title: Up-to-date Interface ID List?
channel.description:
Hey people. It's been a LONG time since I posted a topic. I have no idea where you guys are, so I found a blank 510 client/server and decided to add stuff. I already understand sending stuff and debugging so it should be all good, since I learned a LOT since I left. Now, I'm looking for an Interface ID list. I've already searched, but the one I found was old (Like 5200 was the bank, but sending that crashed the client...)
So is there one out there? Or will I have to experiment and write down my results?
Thanks,
~Lin
